data.text:
Signed booklet: `Heinrich Böll - Nobelpreisträger für Literatur 1972`, published by Kiepenhauer & Witsch, The Nobel Foundation, 1972, softcover booklet, 8,25 x 8,5 inch, 7 pages, in German, signed on the front cover in blue ballpoint ink "Heinrich Böll", with mild signs of wear to the cover - in fine to very fine condition.

All of our pieces are sold with a Certificate of Authenticity. If a piece turns out to be wrong or if you do not like an autograph, you will get your money back for a lifetime.
